            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <del rend="erasure">[<expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> Messio Extricato</del>] <lb n="2"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>ordinar</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan>?</supplied> a s<supplied reason="lost">tudi</supplied>s</del> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> c</supplied><expan><abbr>o</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex cert="low">ulari</ex></expan> comiti <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">amico fidis</supplied>simo <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ann</abbr><ex>onae</ex></expan> pontifi</supplied>ci minori</del> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">p</supplied>raef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praet</abbr><ex>orio</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">Im</supplied>p</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aurelli <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">Antonin</supplied>i Pii Felicis <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan></del> <lb n="9"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>icis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan></supplied> sacerdotis</del> <lb n="10"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">amplissimi</supplied> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan></del> <lb n="11"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">Hermogenes o</supplied>b insignem eius</del> <lb n="12"/><del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">erga se benevol</supplied>entiam qua sibi</del> <lb n="13"/><supplied reason="lost">impetravit in</supplied>dulgentiam <lb n="14"/><supplied reason="lost">sacram benefic</supplied>ii divini honore <lb n="15"/><supplied reason="lost">fulgentem<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> prola</supplied>tis commentariis <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bei der Auffindung waren zwei Fragmente erhalten; Maße beziehen sich auf das linke Fragment; das rechte Fragment scheint verschollen zu sein. Die Tafel gehörte ursprünglich wohl zu einer Statuenbasis im Haus des Massius Extricatus auf dem Esquilin. Datierung: letzte Woche des Jahres 221 (Elagabal wird Oberpriester des Sol Invictus) und dem 11. oder 12.3.222 n. Chr. (Ermordung des Elagabal).</p>
            </div>
